<h1><a name="Updating_to_Release_3"></a>  Updating to Release 3 </h1>
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#About_this_Document"> About this Document</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#Differences_between_OSG_3_RPMs_a"> Differences between OSG 3 RPMs and OSG 1.2 Pacman installations</a>
</li> <li> <a href="?cover=print#List"> List</a>
